reviews.title: Good when it works
reviews.comment: I love having the app and it is a well designed one at that. The $1 deposit fee was a little disappointing at first, but for the convenience I\'m willing to pay. It\'s only a dollar. My problem is the force close on my Rezound if I try to deposit more than one check per session. Have to close the app completely to deposit more than just one.

reviews.title: $1 Deposit Fee?!
reviews.comment: They charge you $1 to make a deposit via your mobile!  I\'ll never use that feature as long as there is a fee and that\'s the whole reason to be excited about a banking app in the first place.  Plenty of bank institutions allow mobile deposits with no fees like Citi, Chase, etc.
